Interestingly, only one study (Perera et al, 2012) in our meta-
analysis used EPA as the sole source for omega-3 supple-
mentation, and showed a significant effect for both inattention
(n = 93, g = 0.69, p = 0.001) and hyperactivity symptoms
(n = 93, g = 1.22, po0.00001).
Of note, n-3 PUFAs have no significant effect on teacher’s
reports
of
